{"tid":270730,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"【分享】挪威•芬蘭•愛沙尼亞","createTime":"2017-06-04T13:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T02:14:59.000Z","uid":14919,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f618a555dd2d7f3fbd96c746c1a65077d6e257","tid":270730,"uid":14919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4271/34703838280_7bf8917459_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4271%2F34703838280_7bf8917459_b.jpg&h=95b3805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(呢篇唔係遊記, 所以我唔會寫好多介紹)<br />\n第一次係連登share旅行相, 大部分相唔係我平時嘅街拍, 而係風景<br />\n所以寫/影得差都唔好插咁大力<br />\n<br />\n啱啱去左挪威, 芬蘭同愛沙尼亞<br />\n前後11日, 而大部分時間都係挪威, 主力去Lofoten Islands<br />\n<br />\n相機: Leica M4<br />\n鏡頭: ZM21 2.8, 六妹, Rigid, 借返黎嘅Minolta 90mm f/4 (去d島一定要帶長焦鏡), 大城市一支35mm夠用<br />\n菲林: Portra 160 <br />\n係Dotwell沖+scan(大jpg)<br />\n<br />\nOslo Opera House - 裏面同外面都有好多值得影嘅嘢同角度, 不過附近d天秤多到避唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4280/35050643666_6a85ccdb7e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4280%2F35050643666_6a85ccdb7e_b.jpg&h=4696511f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4210/35050643326_b50014bec2_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4210%2F35050643326_b50014bec2_b.jpg&h=cd1fd592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超鍾意呢張<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4277/34247011564_b55f6b07a8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4277%2F34247011564_b55f6b07a8_b.jpg&h=8fcaadf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4266/34247012534_feebd0942c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4266%2F34247012534_feebd0942c_b.jpg&h=dd94e75c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOpera House裏面<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4249/34247013854_2477af8066_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4249%2F34247013854_2477af8066_b.jpg&h=2da5da47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4288/34247014314_9fb06d7f64_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4288%2F34247014314_9fb06d7f64_b.jpg&h=11a0be37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4224/34247015024_e8cd0f0aff_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4224%2F34247015024_e8cd0f0aff_b.jpg&h=793e6228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOslo Royal Palace - 好似要暑假先開, 所以淨係係外面影幾張相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4204/34247015724_40bb250db9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4204%2F34247015724_40bb250db9_b.jpg&h=9fc485bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4208/34247016544_b3018a0deb_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4208%2F34247016544_b3018a0deb_b.jpg&h=885f27c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4273/35090500655_2781e2cf62_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4273%2F35090500655_2781e2cf62_b.jpg&h=de41b53a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTim Wendelboe - 飲過最好飲嘅咖啡, 香港無鋪頭比得上佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4214/34247016974_59dd182eb9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4214%2F34247016974_59dd182eb9_b.jpg&h=c3981e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSupreme Roastwork - 都唔錯, 不過無Tim咁好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4290/35090500995_c05805230a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4290%2F35090500995_c05805230a_b.jpg&h=871837a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後有d Oslo街頭嘅相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4202/34703834390_b759e148b0_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4202%2F34703834390_b759e148b0_b.jpg&h=7fb60457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4288/34247066314_e255a3ec41_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4288%2F34247066314_e255a3ec41_b.jpg&h=2f7ce2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4257/34703834820_f81d3a7e1b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4257%2F34703834820_f81d3a7e1b_b.jpg&h=b7a51684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4198/34247067124_8173c6af3d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4198%2F34247067124_8173c6af3d_b.jpg&h=d3956fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"7d67fbee5c955cc3fcb37475e97cafc4813fe29b","tid":270730,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"巴打，我遲下都去愛沙尼亞同瑞典，巴打有冇去啲有菲林機賣嘅市集？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81501a4bbe03ce825c533a83dd46e369259a1590","tid":270730,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:23:37.000Z","msg":"第一張好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419273adfdc751d3dabf45ff118e0f370e4f8e60","tid":270730,"uid":14919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:45:13.000Z","msg":"去Oslo兩日之後就飛去Lofoten Islands, 搭呢架螺旋槳飛機20分鐘, delay左3個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4202/34703835420_2797fd5f20_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4202%2F34703835420_2797fd5f20_b.jpg&h=2176797c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機塊玻璃好污糟 影咩都有霧咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4277/34703835960_ffcbb8bb52_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4277%2F34703835960_ffcbb8bb52_b.jpg&h=2f200060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4281/35090501615_45bf707971_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4281%2F35090501615_45bf707971_b.jpg&h=d14b448e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿途成日都會停車影相 不過菲林機無geotag 所以都唔記得係邊度影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4224/34247068404_bf1c4c9cdd_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4224%2F34247068404_bf1c4c9cdd_b.jpg&h=3e4be651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多雪山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4259/34703836310_f4f88325f8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4259%2F34703836310_f4f88325f8_b.jpg&h=240192b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRamberg - 一個幾出名嘅白沙灘<br />\n呢張行上左少少個山影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4241/34247069844_6770d520c5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4241%2F34247069844_6770d520c5_b.jpg&h=dd75e73c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4220/34703836630_62cbbe89f1_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4220%2F34703836630_62cbbe89f1_b.jpg&h=598b5ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落沙灘條路<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4206/34926515012_92d8ffd0c5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4206%2F34926515012_92d8ffd0c5_b.jpg&h=3de24dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4215/34703836900_d168baf744_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4215%2F34703836900_d168baf744_b.jpg&h=116caaea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4275/35050705436_05649a65c5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4275%2F35050705436_05649a65c5_b.jpg&h=1468fdf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好鍾意呢張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4252/35050706306_eb3896dcc1_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4252%2F35050706306_eb3896dcc1_b.jpg&h=7d9fceb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRamberg附近嘅一條橋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4259/34703837190_c896ec22e9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4259%2F34703837190_c896ec22e9_b.jpg&h=28b1762a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA - 個島最南嘅地方 不過真係無咩特別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4251/35050707606_90fe714489_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4251%2F35050707606_90fe714489_b.jpg&h=edce6790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4229/34247019894_05a4a22919_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4229%2F34247019894_05a4a22919_b.jpg&h=0610601e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多紅色嘅漁屋 好似唔少都租出去俾遊客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4243/35050708246_c3e532d3f8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4243%2F35050708246_c3e532d3f8_b.jpg&h=075eaf94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超多呢d曬鱈魚嘅架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4226/34247020724_b7bfc82bd5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4226%2F34247020724_b7bfc82bd5_b.jpg&h=6d12a42f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74d3b501515181071691242111b4effbcf897cdc","tid":270730,"uid":14919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，我遲下都去愛沙尼亞同瑞典，巴打有冇去啲有菲林機賣嘅市集？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係塔林即日來回, 所以無咩留意<br />\n不過我係一間書店見到三四部俄佬機<br />\n都幾殘下 返黎一定要抹油<br />\n不過就15-20歐就有"},{"pid":"452478777a762a65c81b7d3c3cbea463d22a2cea","tid":270730,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去Oslo兩日之後就飛去Lofoten Islands, 搭呢架螺旋槳飛機20分鐘, delay左3個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4202/34703835420_2797fd5f20_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4202%2F34703835420_2797fd5f20_b.jpg&h=2176797c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機塊玻璃好污糟 影咩都有霧咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4277/34703835960_ffcbb8bb52_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4277%2F34703835960_ffcbb8bb52_b.jpg&h=2f200060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4281/35090501615_45bf707971_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4281%2F35090501615_45bf707971_b.jpg&h=d14b448e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿途成日都會停車影相 不過菲林機無geotag 所以都唔記得係邊度影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4224/34247068404_bf1c4c9cdd_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4224%2F34247068404_bf1c4c9cdd_b.jpg&h=3e4be651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多雪山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4259/34703836310_f4f88325f8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4259%2F34703836310_f4f88325f8_b.jpg&h=240192b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRamberg - 一個幾出名嘅白沙灘<br />\n呢張行上左少少個山影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4241/34247069844_6770d520c5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4241%2F34247069844_6770d520c5_b.jpg&h=dd75e73c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4220/34703836630_62cbbe89f1_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4220%2F34703836630_62cbbe89f1_b.jpg&h=598b5ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落沙灘條路<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4206/34926515012_92d8ffd0c5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4206%2F34926515012_92d8ffd0c5_b.jpg&h=3de24dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4215/34703836900_d168baf744_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4215%2F34703836900_d168baf744_b.jpg&h=116caaea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4275/35050705436_05649a65c5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4275%2F35050705436_05649a65c5_b.jpg&h=1468fdf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好鍾意呢張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4252/35050706306_eb3896dcc1_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4252%2F35050706306_eb3896dcc1_b.jpg&h=7d9fceb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRamberg附近嘅一條橋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4259/34703837190_c896ec22e9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4259%2F34703837190_c896ec22e9_b.jpg&h=28b1762a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA - 個島最南嘅地方 不過真係無咩特別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4251/35050707606_90fe714489_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4251%2F35050707606_90fe714489_b.jpg&h=edce6790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4229/34247019894_05a4a22919_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4229%2F34247019894_05a4a22919_b.jpg&h=0610601e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多紅色嘅漁屋 好似唔少都租出去俾遊客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4243/35050708246_c3e532d3f8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4243%2F35050708246_c3e532d3f8_b.jpg&h=075eaf94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超多呢d曬鱈魚嘅架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4226/34247020724_b7bfc82bd5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4226%2F34247020724_b7bfc82bd5_b.jpg&h=6d12a42f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾年前見過有巴打去lofoten island, 結果exchange個陣去左，不過個陣11月，好彩無落大雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解你會揀呢到去？ 有無去reine?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81d88f41d1494b96a1a67a67b475f1d5e0cbe7b","tid":270730,"uid":14919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去Oslo兩日之後就飛去Lofoten Islands, 搭呢架螺旋槳飛機20分鐘, delay左3個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4202/34703835420_2797fd5f20_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4202%2F34703835420_2797fd5f20_b.jpg&h=2176797c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機塊玻璃好污糟 影咩都有霧咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4277/34703835960_ffcbb8bb52_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4277%2F34703835960_ffcbb8bb52_b.jpg&h=2f200060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticfli